  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 3rd June 2025</p>

  <p>We collect basic personal info (like your name, Instagram handle, phone number, or email) only when you share it with us. For example, to get in touch, start training, or follow up.</p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Name, contact info (email, phone, @handle)</li>
    <li>Info you provide through forms (like training goals)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How we use it</h2>
